{"id":140309,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：藏族喇嘛四川自焚死引抗议/","date":"2011-03-17T07:30:30Z","modified":"2011-03-17T07:30:30Z","title":"简讯：藏族喇嘛四川自焚死引抗议","content":"<div>\n<p>中国四川阿坝一名藏族喇嘛自焚抗议藏区骚乱三周年，他的死亡引发当地小规模抗议。</p>\n<p>这名21岁的喇嘛名叫盘措（音译），来自格尔登寺。</p>\n<p>流亡藏人表示，在盘措自焚丧生后，阿坝大约有1000人上街示威，并且与军警发生冲突。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/awT6_VAJ9NY_HU5HIjzaHg1ndZo/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/awT6_VAJ9NY_HU5HIjzaHg1ndZo/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/awT6_VAJ9NY_HU5HIjzaHg1ndZo/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/awT6_VAJ9NY_HU5HIjzaHg1ndZo/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=f7gGUmb4XSY:t_fXFgPi2a4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/f7gGUmb4XSY\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):ziyouhulianwangATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9432,